Description:
Perfect Beach house!
Located in a sleepy corner of Cowes, this property presents great value for your money.
Positioned on a 603m2 approx. block. There are 4 bedrooms, master with ensuite and BIR’s in all rooms.
The open plan kitchen living opens up unto the rear north facing decking area. Covered by sails, you can retreat to the deck to soak up the north facing aspect.
There is a coonara wood fire and a split system heating/cooling system in the main living area. Polished floorboards throughout the living and carpet in all the bedrooms.
This property would make the perfect weekend escape retreat or a permanent home. Close to both red rocks and Ventnor beaches – inspections are a must.

Description:
Filled With Character And Charm
Located in a quiet court location this immaculate home is the perfect place to call home.
Featuring large open plan main living area with polished floors and high ceilings throughout opening onto a fantastic covered entertaining area. Quality kitchen with large stainless oven and dishwasher and timber benches.
There is also a second living area perfect for the kids and a separate study that could also easily be used as a 4th bedroom or guest room.
Adding 3 bedrooms with built in robes the master with walk in robe and ensuite it suits a range of buyers.
To finish off the perfect package there is a double garage, cosy wood fire, ducted vacuum and beautiful gardens. Inspection a must.

Description:
Location and Lifestyle!
This is your opportunity to secure a great investment / lifestyle, double storey townhouse in the heart of Cowes. With the magnificent north facing beach and shopping precinct all within a short stroll, this brilliantly positioned townhouse allows you to do away with the car and explore the shops, restaurants, bars and amenities at your leisure.
The lovely light-filled lower level features a large open plan living, kitchen and dining area that flows onto an undercover outdoor balcony overlooking the courtyard garden, as well as a separate guest powder room and internal access to the single garage.
The second level of this spacious townhouse includes a second comfortable lounge/living area with access to a north facing private terrace, huge dual access bathroom including corner spa, separate shower and double basin vanity and two bedrooms with built in robes.
Other great features include two split system heating/cooling units, dishwasher, single garage with laundry and access to the courtyard, fully fenced. Currently operating as a holiday rental, the choice of use is yours.
This property for sale in Cowes is proudly presented to you by Ray White Real Estate Phillip Island

Description:
LOW MAINTENANCE AND MODERN
This stunning apartment in Central Cowes of generous proportions has wonderful surprises at every turn. You can walk to everything and enjoy all that the township of Cowes on Phillip Island has to offer. This is one of only three apartments on the block, with a large courtyard, undercover deck & single garage.
Featuring beautiful timber floors, a modern open plan kitchen, living and dining area with large windows filling the home with light. The ground floor also contains the master bedroom with walk in robe, ensuite and laundry. Upstairs are a further 2 bedrooms, a large family room with balcony and bathroom with separate toilet.
Each room has its own split system reverse cycle air conditioner.
Inspection will impress! Great for a low maintenance permanent home, would be an ideal holiday rental or permanent rental for investment purposes.

Description:

A new release of extra large home sites situated around an exclusive cul-de-sac, including land with bay views and acre lots set amongst mature eucalypts.

This fantastic studio apartment is located in a prime position across the road from the renowned ‘Lovers Walk’ beach and foreshore playground and only a short stroll to Cowes shopping/ restaurant precinct. This apartment has everything to offer at your doorstep.
Located on the second floor, close to the elevator and stairs. The apartment comes completely furnished with kitchenette featuring fridge, microwave and hotplate, bathroom with spa and separate shower, a dining/living area that doubles as a second bedroom with two single beds and a master bedroom with sitting area that opens onto the balcony taking in the lovely bay view. Currently managed by our holiday rental department, This would make the ideal investment or holiday escape.

Description:
Enjoy The Indoor And Outdoor Lifestyle!
Situated in the family friendly Shearwater Estate boasting a lovely Northerly aspect is this sizeable single level brick home ideal for permanent or holiday living.
Comprising a spacious open plan living, kitchen and dining area, a second formal living zone, four robed bedrooms and two bathrooms, the master is complete with a walk in robe and ensuite
Additional features include split system heating and cooling, combustion heater, stone bench top, glass splashbacks, 900mm stainless steel gas cooktop and electric oven to kitchen, solar power and ample storage.
The expansive outdoor undercover entertainment area flows off both living areas and is sure to impress all buyers and comes complete with bench space, a sink and built in BBQ.
The home also offers a large double garage with internal access in addition to the double gates at the side of the property allowing access for trailors/boats or the caravan. At the rear of the property there is a shed with a manual roller door, lights and power that could be utilised as a studio/man cave or teenagers retreat.
Set on a 634sqm approx fenced allotment with low maintenance landscaped surrounds this property is within easy walking distance to the Cowes Golf Club, Local supermarkets, Cowes Primary School, Doctors, Town Centre and the Pristine North facing Silverleaves Beach.

Description:
STUNNING CONTEMPORARY HOME IN TRANQUIL LOCATION
Located in a quiet court, this stunning property is central to Red Rocks Beach and provides a tranquil rural view over the golf ranch.
Immaculately presented, the home is modern with an ambiance of sophistication. The lower level offers a dedicated study, stylish modern kitchen with stainless steel appliances and generous walk in pantry, stunning dining and lounge zone with double height ceilings and bi-fold doors, and a very private master bedroom with walk in robe, en-suite and beautiful lush carpets. An extensive north-facing deck can be accessed from the master bedroom and through the bi-fold doors extending from the lounge and dining zone. The upper level provides an additional 3 spacious bedrooms, 2 with built in robes and corner desks, surrounding a central bathroom. The home is exceptional with stunning timber flooring, extensive north-facing windows, split system heating and cooling, ceiling fans and stunning light fittings.
The property is fully fenced with extensive established landscaping, watertanks, generous north-facing deck with counter leaver umbrella for shade, remote double garage and additional parking for boat or caravan storage.
Quiet and exclusive, this stunning property is only a short distance from popular Red Rocks Beach and central Cowes, and only a short distance from all of Phillip Island’s many attractions. Invest or reside, this impressive property is waiting for you to enjoy. Arrange your inspection today.
